headline: Better Nuclear Income Play for 2026: Cameco vs. Duke Energy
summary: Cameco and Duke Energy both make a compelling case for a nuclear energy investment, but one of them is a much better dividend play.

headline: Here's What to Expect From Duke Energy's Next Earnings Report
summary: Duke Energy is scheduled to announce its fiscal fourth-quarter earnings next month, and analysts project a single-digit earnings drop.

headline: Piedmont Natural Gas shares tips to help lower energy costs before upcoming cold weather
summary: As temperatures drop across the Southeast this weekend and into next week, causing heating systems to work harder and use more energy, Piedmont Natural Gas offers tips, resources and assistance programs to help customers stay comfortable while managing seasonal energy bills.

headline: Duke Energy helps customers stay energy smart as temperatures plunge with programs and tips to save money and energy
summary: As a surge of winter cold sweeps in, Duke Energy is committed to helping customers manage energy costs during the coldest months of the year. Historically, January is the peak for energy use as heating systems work harder to keep homes comfortable.
